==Getting started==
===Searching the armour chest===
* {{tbox|The chest is securely locked.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil===
* '''Player:''' Hi there. Looks like you're in some trouble.
* '''Lady Servil:''' The cart? That's the least of my problems. I've got to find my family...
* {{tbox|Before starting this quest, be aware that your combat level is lower than the recommended level of 50.}}
* {{tselect|Start the Fight Arena quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' Your family? Can I help?
** '''Lady Servil:''' You'd be willing to?
** '''Player:''' Of course. Tell me what happened.
** '''Lady Servil:''' Well, I'm Lady Servil. I was travelling to Ardougne with my husband, Justin, and son, Sammy, when our cart broke on some rocks.
** '''Lady Servil:''' Some of General Khazard's men spotted us and offered to help, but they demanded my husband and son fight in their arena first! We said no, but they took them anyway!
** '''Player:''' General Khazard?
** '''Lady Servil:''' He's a menace! This entire area is under the control of him and his mercenary group, the Khazard Army. They prey on the weak and vulnerable, making them fight in that arena of theirs, all for entertainment!
** '''Player:''' That's horrible! How are they able to get away with it?
** '''Lady Servil:''' The authorities don't care. Khazard's men just pay them off if they ever come to investigate.
** '''Player:''' Well they won't stop me. I'm going to try my best to find your family.
** '''Lady Servil:''' Thank you. They'll be somewhere inside the arena. I'll be waiting here for you.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** '''Player:''' Well I hope it works out. Good luck.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil after starting the quest===
* '''Lady Servil:''' Adventurer, please... bring back my family. They'll be somewhere inside the arena.
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'll find them.
* {{tact|end}}

