===Talking to Hengrad in the jail cell===
* '''Hengrad:''' Hello there. So Khazard got his hands on you too?
* '''Player:''' Unfortunately so.
* '''Hengrad:''' Well if you're lucky, you might last as long as me.
* '''Player:''' How long have you been here?
* '''Hengrad:''' As long as I can remember. I was a child when his men kidnapped me. My whole life has been spent killing and fighting, all in the hope that one day I might escape.
* '''Player:''' Don't give up.
* '''Hengrad:''' Thanks, friend.
* '''Hengrad:''' Wait... sounds like the guard is coming. Looks like you'll be going back into the arena. Good luck, friend.
* {{qact|The player is brought into the arena.}}
* '''General Khazard:''' Now watch closely, friends. I fear this may be where your protector dies.
* '''Justin Servil:''' Ignore him! You can do it!
* {{tact|end}}

