* '''General Khazard:''' You proved yourself in battle against me. That is something few can boast of. For that, you may leave. However, if you ever oppose me again, I won't hesitate to wipe you from existence!
* '''General Khazard:''' Now go. I have business to attend to elsewhere that is far more important than you.
* {{tact|end}}

